---
description: Django/DRF backend rules for files under apps/api.
globs:
  - "apps/api/**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

Before editing backend code:
- Read apps/api/AGENTS.md.
- Follow Django 5.2, DRF, PostgreSQL, Celery, Redis, Channels, Pydantic, OpenAPI conventions.
- Keep business logic in services/selectors where appropriate.
- Add or update tests with every behavior change.
